gentoo-penguins-may-actually-be-four-different-species-scientists-say-revealing-theyre-not-quite-winners-of-climate-change-after-all-180988769/</guid></item><item><title>螃蟹什么时候进化出标志性的侧身飞艇？科学家将其追溯到 2 亿年前的共同祖先</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/when-did-crabs-evolve-their-iconic-sideways-scuttle-scientist-traced-it-to-a-200-million-year-old-common-ancestor-180988765/</link><description>研究结果表明，它们著名的横向运动只进化过一次。它可能帮助动物迅速扩散和多样化，因为向两个方向移动意味着它们可以轻松逃脱捕食者</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 May 2026 15:57:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/when-did-crabs-evolve-their-iconic-sideways-scuttle-scientist-traced-it-to-a-200-million-year-old-common-ancestor-180988765/</guid></item><item><title>一项新研究表明，定期穿着降温背心可能会帮助您减少体内脂肪</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/regularly-wearing-a-cooling-vest-might-help-you-lose-body-fat-according-to-a-new-study-180988767/</link><description>超重或肥胖的参与者每天早上佩戴这些配件两个小时，持续六周，平均减重两磅。研究人员怀疑在冷水中淋浴或游泳可能会产生类似的效果</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 May 2026 13:11:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/regularly-wearing-a-cooling-vest-might-help-you-lose-body-fat-according-to-a-new-study-180988767/</guid></item><item><title>这只野狗很可能被袋鼠踢了一脚，但在 500 年来一直尊重它的原住民社区的帮助下，它在千年前就痊愈了</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/likely-kicked-by-a-kangaroo-this-dingo-healed-a-millennium-ago-thanks-to-help-from-an-aboriginal-community-that-continued-to-honor-it-for-500-years-180988768/</link><description>新的研究表明，澳大利亚巴金吉人的祖先在野狗死后的几个世纪里，如何按照仪式将河蚌壳添加到墓地，这表明他们对它非常关心</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 May 2026 21:06:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/likely-kicked-by-a-kangaroo-this-dingo-healed-a-millennium-ago-thanks-to-help-from-an-aboriginal-community-that-continued-to-honor-it-for-500-years-180988768/</guid></item><item><title>大英博物馆准备将这件杰作平放，贝叶挂毯开启全新视角之旅</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/the-bayeux-tapestry-takes-a-journey-for-a-fresh-perspective-as-the-british-museum-prepares-to-lay-the-masterpiece-out-flat-180988764/</link><description>在法国度过了几个世纪之后，这幅描绘诺曼征服英格兰的 1000 年历史的挂毯正在回到自己的祖国</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 May 2026 20:09:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/the-bayeux-tapestry-takes-a-journey-for-a-fresh-perspective-as-the-british-museum-prepares-to-lay-the-masterpiece-out-flat-180988764/</guid></item><item><title>“反灭绝”公司表示，它用人造鸡蛋孵化出小鸡，为复活渡渡鸟和其他灭绝的鸟类铺平了道路</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/de-extinction-company-says-it-hatched-chicks-from-artificial-eggs-paving-the-way-for-resurrecting-dodos-and-other-bygone-birds-180988766/</link><description>Colossal Biosciences 宣布 3D 打印的蜂窝结构中诞生了 26 只活的小鸡。但该公司不打算在论文中详细介绍该系统，其使命也面临批评</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 May 2026 20:09:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/de-extinction-company-says-it-hatched-chicks-from-artificial-eggs-paving-the-way-for-resurrecting-dodos-and-other-bygone-birds-180988766/</guid></item><item><title>为什么这位古罗马士兵的墓碑隐藏在路易斯安那州的后院？考古学家解开了这个谜团，并帮助将文物送回意大利</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/why-was-this-ancient-roman-soldiers-gravestone-hidden-in-a-louisiana-backyard-archaeologists-solved-the-mystery-and-helped-return-the-artifact-to-italy-180988761/</link><description>去年在新奥尔良一处房产上出现的墓碑曾经属于一名去世于近 2000 年前的罗马士兵。官员们最近在罗马举行的仪式上归还了这块石头</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 May 2026 18:30:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/why-was-this-ancient-roman-soldiers-gravestone-hidden-in-a-louisiana-backyard-archaeologists-solved-the-mystery-and-helped-return-the-artifact-to-italy-180988761/</guid></item><item><title>《蒙娜丽莎》要搬到新家了。卢浮宫刚刚宣布了将设计她的私人套房的建筑师</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/mona-lisa-is-moving-to-a-new-home-the-louvre-just-announced-the-architects-who-will-design-her-private-suite-180988763/</link><descr